{"type":null,"faqId":18682,"title":"如何启用屏幕解锁图案？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.27708334in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.16944444in;margin-left:0.8784722in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span class=\"s2\">设置 &gt;隐私和安全&gt;屏幕安全保护&gt;解锁样式&gt; 图案。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>在“选择您的图案”界面，通过手指在屏幕连续划过几个圆的圆心设定解锁时使用的图形样式，再点击“继续”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>再次在屏幕上划过刚才的样式，点击“确认”完成解锁图形的设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4.  </span><span>当点电源键或开关机时，手机会默认进入图案解锁界面，在该界面划过刚才的图案样式，进行解锁。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1746","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422260329000,"seriesProductName":"Cherry-CL10,CherryPlus-TL00,CherryPlus-TL00H,CherryPlus-TL00M,CherryPlus-TL10,CherryPlus-UL00,CherryPlus-UL10","visitedTimes":123,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}